name: 2 DAY 1 NIGHT GILI LABAK ISLAND TOUR
description:
Gili Labak is a small island that located
 in southeast side of Puteran island, the capital city of Puteran island
 or Madura island. Administratively, this island is in Talango 
sub-district, Sumenep regency, East Java. This small island is covered 
only 5 hectares and there are 35 families live in this island. For those
 who visit this island can explore the whole island over the beach. The 
inhabitants are living by sea products for the land is not that fertile 
to be planted. For you that loves to enjoy snorkling or beach activity, 
you have to live this place by yourself!!
